name: Greeting Cards - The Language of Flowers - Series 1
description:

The "Language of Flowers" Greeting Cards, comes with 4 specially selected Botanical Portraits. Printed on a thick lustrous matte card. Blank on the inside for your personal expression. Perfect for any occasion because flowers speak the language of love.
